data.description: Step into this magnificent waterfront residence situated on the picturesque shores of Lake Norman. Upon entering, you'll be welcomed by a generously proportioned foyer that leads to an expansive living space showcasing oversized windows that frame the breathtaking waterfront views. The well-appointed gourmet kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and seamless access to the sprawling deck that affords commanding views of the lake. Enjoy morning coffee in your main-level primary suite overlooking beautiful Lake Norman. The upper level is dedicated to three bedrooms and two bathrooms, with an open loft area that gazes down upon the foyer below. Outside, a fully fenced yard encompasses an oversized multi-level deck, lush landscaping, and a private dock. This property offers an oasis of privacy and tranquility, all the while maintaining the utmost convenience, just minutes from shopping, dining, and entertainment options that Mooresville has to offer.
